title: Great 2 bedroom unit
posting_body: ['Very nice 2 unit Available 9/1  is upstairs unit of a fourplex.', 'Nice quiet building in a great area.', 'Very accessible to getting to Uptown, Midtown, Downtown and close to Light rail, Hiawatha Ave and many Highways.', ' Unit is hardwood floors recently refinished and has a lot of chachacter woodwork.', 'Has a large kitchen with re-finished sink and newer stove.', 'Has large bedrooms.', 'Next to a community garden with plots available and across from a large park.', 'New water heater and gas meter and has a programable thermostat so is an very efficient unit.', ' Washer/Dryer and plenty of storage on site.', 'Bathroom remodeled.', 'Water, trash, and sewer.', 'all paid.', 'Two off street parking spots come with the unit.', '$1,450.00', 'Please call or text', 'show contact info', 'and leave message with your info.']
